description:
&lt;p&gt;We have an exciting opportunity for an enthusiastic and customer focused individual to join our friendly and busy Recruitment and On Boarding team within the Workforce Division.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Supported by the Recruitment Team Leader, you will be responsible for undertaking safe and fair recruitment, maintaining a customer focused approach while responding to a high volume of queries, ensuring that all candidates have a positive recruitment and onboarding experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A demonstrable background in high volume administration and experience of providing first class customer service is essential. A flexible working attitude is required, along with the ability to work to changing demands and priorities. You will embrace the challenge of working in a demanding environment where attention to detail is essential. Experience with NHS recruitment would be advantageous.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;In return, we will support your professional development and provide on-going support and training.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be based in Wallington, with travel to Sutton and Chelsea when required.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Amanda Standfield, Recruitment Team Lead, amanda.standfield@rmh.nhs.uk, 020 8661 3031&lt;/p&gt;
